{"tid":1003570,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"求意見 想帶媽媽去意大利旅行 唔跟團","createTime":"2019-01-31T17:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T18:38:34.000Z","uid":90448,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1cde2eb7204b1e4612328f78ff58612d2329e117","tid":1003570,"uid":90448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T17:59:34.000Z","msg":"以後冇錢帶屋企人去玩<br />\n而家畢咗業一年 收入都算穩定<br />\n想今年/出年帶媽媽去意大利（威尼斯+佛羅倫斯）<br />\n<br />\n機票 酒店 $15000？<br />\n其他洗費 $10000 玩7日夠唔夠?<br />\n<br />\n因為媽媽冇出過遠門 <br />\n諗緊好唔好同佢跟團<br />\n我自己以前exchange去過意大利玩<br />\n但唔識意大利文 所以都唔知好唔好同佢2個人去玩 <br />\n好似幾危險 驚比人偷嘢<br />\n<br />\n巴打們點睇？"},{"pid":"51e4e9810e1d0e9bfb19a440aa899ed5e9a89ff5","tid":1003570,"uid":78429,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"記得帶多幾個後備銀包俾扒手偷"},{"pid":"227b9de4c229e4a80781572234d221b3a7bfef7f","tid":1003570,"uid":90448,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"51e4e9810e1d0e9bfb19a440aa899ed5e9a89ff5","tid":1003570,"uid":78429,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"記得帶多幾個後備銀包俾扒手偷"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T18:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係要擺假嘅銀包<br />\n周街都係賊 <br />\n我超唔鐘意意大利 <br />\n去咗7日 日日都比人偷幾次嘢<br />\n好彩冇事 當時窮遊"},{"pid":"57e96ff06b298aaeef4a0a0c7902c610c2291f75","tid":1003570,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"227b9de4c229e4a80781572234d221b3a7bfef7f","tid":1003570,"uid":90448,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"51e4e9810e1d0e9bfb19a440aa899ed5e9a89ff5","tid":1003570,"uid":78429,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"記得帶多幾個後備銀包俾扒手偷"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T18:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係要擺假嘅銀包<br />\n周街都係賊 <br />\n我超唔鐘意意大利 <br />\n去咗7日 日日都比人偷幾次嘢<br />\n好彩冇事 當時窮遊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T18:07:33.000Z","msg"