c=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T03:58:14.000Z","msg":"咁咪去瑞意"},{"pid":"60783a7e5f1ba82af9af4be4cb5318ff818da060","tid":1003570,"uid":79662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c93e2613f55a3b304a7c72784c0cd55f933baff","tid":1003570,"uid":90448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"427a91b9fee343692db40c292753ce15a5dd186a","tid":1003570,"uid":79662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T20:31:33.000Z","msg":"Venice&gt; florence有2個鐘快車italo<br />\n又快又靚 唔算好貴，好似20歐一個人<br />\nFlorence 3-4 日（睇你行唔行啲museum)<br />\nVenice 2-3日夠 <br />\n<br />\n可以係Florence 果時比半日去睇pisa個塔<br />\n啲娘親多數都鐘意睇出名既境點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T00:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔行博物館 老母唔睇畫 <br />\n佢鐘意睇景 同行當地鋪頭（唔係名牌）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:06:18.000Z","msg":"咁可能venice可以留多日， <br />\n去埋彩虹島同玻璃島 <br />\n但只可以講依邊無咩當地鋪 <br />\n好多都大陸人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFlorence最好住火車站果頭 / 近duomo<br />\n依啲我上次去點既地點 <br />\n睇下你有無用啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6D74aKw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6D74aKw.png&h=3a76c5f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nVenice最好住我圈果到 <br />\n下面好貴 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rt9ifbr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRt9ifbr.png&h=760b4a34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVenice個城好易迷路，但都係種樂趣黎<br />\n<br />\n啲地點我都係自己去果時做reference<br />\n唔係話好齊"},{"pid":"a261ff345ec18c4cab2fd38a1fbdc2f2a25393ad","tid":1003570,"uid":79662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"214a26b658c20a738e9a6b8d308bb1f7797e68a4","tid":1003570,"uid":90448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"127969f5e1e1c20baca89b77feb65a234d6c5ae0","tid":1003570,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:31:41.000Z","msg":"係你想去意大利，定你阿媽想去啊<br />\n<br />\n老人家唔會想去依類地方應該"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"媽媽想去啊<br />\n佢冇去過外國 佢鐘意睇風景<br />\n佢仲想去瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"想睇風景咁瑞士好啲啵<br />\n意大利係城景 無咩山水<br />\n但瑞士好貴.. 草多陣錢先<br />\n無可能窮遊到 水餐廳成5歐1L<br />\n每餐起麻2-300起跳<br />\n（無可能叫娘親食kabab ga)<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n瑞士我會提意<br />\n去Grindelwald instead of interlaken<br />\n同上少女峰<br />\n但無記錯上一上去都成千幾2千銀<br />\n<br />\n我上次去左10日買8day pass <br />\n入門都要成380歐<br />\n<br />\n意大利出發<br />\nBrig- chur（glacier express)<br />\nzurich( arth goldau- lucerne)<br />\nBern- interlaken - 住grindelwald上少女蜂<br />\nBrienz 蒸氣火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再去zermatt( 個城太旅遊化 我覺得唔洗去） <br />\n娘親比我chur到叫救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 全程坐火車 睇境 但要好小心plan<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意大利就是但去個城睇就得<br />\n簡單方便"}]}